channel.title: NoobX , Noobs Welcome. [ Beta Test ]
channel.description:
[b]Hello, I have been working on a private server for a little while now. Its not quite finished yet, so therefore. I just want to have a couple players online, to see how it does with players.
NoobX, is just a little server that you can play with your friends, theres alot of freedom. There will only be a couple staff members due to freedom. I want the players to have alot of freedom so that they feel welcome in the game. Although players, that disobey this, will be punished. I want the player to have a fair chance at everything, not just couple people.
Also, I need some Beta Testers. Please and Thank you. [/b] Bug Report:
[ul][li]Username:[/li] [li]Bug(Explain):[/li][/ul]
Send bug report to: [email]typrizza@live.com[/email]
